HAdo 1.1.0

• New list icon picker with direct `mdi:*` search, live preview, and inline suggestions
• Emoji and MDI list icons can sync to Home Assistant when admin rights allow it; custom images stay local-only
• Reopening the picker now restores the active icon choice, and resetting returns to the native default list icon
• Pull-to-refresh in every list editor plus smoother scrolling and item-state updates
• Security: updated Glance library to fix a protobuf vulnerability (CVE-2024-7254)
